@startuml
title Object lifecycle: Discord message delivery attempt
[*] --> Pending : delivery requested
Pending --> Skipped : missing active class, guild, channel, or Discord identity
Pending --> ResolvingRecipient : recipient has guild context
ResolvingRecipient --> Failed : recipient cannot be resolved
ResolvingRecipient --> Sending : Discord user/channel resolved
Sending --> Sent : Discord REST call succeeds
Sending --> Failed : Discord REST call fails
Skipped --> [*]
Sent --> [*]
Failed --> [*]
@enduml
